<p>Not all Airbnb management companies offer the same level of service. When choosing a property manager in Melaka, you'll typically encounter two main models: <strong>Full-Service Management</strong> and <strong>Bare (or Basic) Management</strong>.</p>

<p>But what's the real difference? And more importantly, which approach aligns with your investment goals, budget, and involvement preference?</p>

<p>Let's break down both models with real numbers and examples from iHousing's experience managing 100+ Melaka properties.</p>

<h2>What is Full-Service Management?</h2>

<h3>Complete End-to-End Service</h3>

<p>Full-service management (what iHousing offers) means we handle <strong>everything</strong> related to your Airbnb:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Listing creation</strong> - Professional photos, compelling descriptions, optimized titles</li>
<li><strong>Multi-platform distribution</strong> - Airbnb, Booking.com, Agoda, Expedia, VRBO</li>
<li><strong>Guest communication</strong> - quick response during business hours to inquiries and issues</li>
<li><strong>Check-in/check-out</strong> - Guest greeting, key exchange, orientation</li>
<li><strong>Cleaning coordination</strong> - Scheduling, quality control, restocking supplies</li>
<li><strong>Maintenance management</strong> - Repairs, renovations, preventative maintenance</li>
<li><strong>Pricing optimization</strong> - Dynamic pricing, seasonal adjustments, rate strategy</li>
<li><strong>Review management</strong> - Proactive review requests, response to feedback</li>
<li><strong>Financial reporting</strong> - Monthly statements, revenue tracking, expense breakdown</li>
<li><strong>Legal compliance</strong> - MOTAC license, strata rules, local regulations</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Your involvement:</strong> Zero to 2 hours per month (review reports, approve major expenses).</p>

<h2>What is Bare (Basic) Management?</h2>

<h3>Minimum Viable Service</h3>

<p>Bare management covers only the essentials:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Listing on Airbnb only</strong> - Single platform, basic setup</li>
<li><strong>Guest inquiries</strong> - Basic Q&A, limited availability</li>
<li><strong>Check-in coordination</strong> - Key handoff, minimal interaction</li>
<li><strong>Cleaning arrangement</strong> - Schedule cleaners (you pay separately)</li>
<li><strong>Payout processing</strong> - Collect money, transfer to you</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Your involvement:</strong> 10-15 hours per month (maintenance, supplies, guest issues, pricing updates).</p>

<p><strong>What's NOT included:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li>No multi-platform listing</li>
<li>No dynamic pricing (you set rates, they don't change)</li>
<li>No professional photography</li>
<li>No maintenance coordination (you handle repairs)</li>
<li>No supply restocking (you buy and replace)</li>
<li>No review management</li>
<li>Limited guest support (business hours only)</li>
</ul>

