<h2>Which Fits Your Investment Style?</h2>

<h3>Choose Full-Service If You:</h3>

<ul>
<li><strong>Want hands-off investment</strong> - Zero involvement preferred</li>
<li><strong>Live outside Melaka</strong> - Can't handle local issues personally</li>
<li><strong>Value professional optimization</strong> - Want maximum revenue</li>
