</ul>

<h3>Choose Bare Management If You:</h3>

<ul>
<li><strong>Live in Melaka nearby</strong> - Can quickly handle issues</li>
<li><strong>Enjoy hands-on involvement</strong> - Like hospitality, want to stay involved</li>
<li><strong>Have limited budget</strong> - Can't afford full-service fees (but see ROI above)</li>
