<h2>Questions to Ask Any Management Company</h2>

<h3>Determine Their Service Level</h3>

<p>Before signing, ask:</p>

<ol>
<li><strong>"What's included in your base fee?"</strong> - Look for hidden add-ons</li>
<li><strong>"How many platforms do you list on?"</strong> - Should be 4-5 minimum</li>
<li><strong>"Who handles guest emergencies at late-night?"</strong> - Need responsive coverage</li>
<li><strong>"How often do you update pricing?"</strong> - Should be dynamic/daily</li>
<li><strong>"Do you mark up cleaning or supplies?"</strong> - Should be cost price</li>
<li><strong>"Can I see sample monthly reports?"</strong> - Transparency matters</li>
<li><strong>"What's your average owner occupancy rate?"</strong> - Should be 60%+</li>
<li><strong>"How long is your contract?"</strong> - Avoid 12+ month lock-ins</li>
</ol>

